A customer has a large campus facility and needs to connect storage in two different
buildings that are 1 km apart. Which of the following cables would be used?
A. SAS
B. SCSI
C. Single-mode fiber
D. Multi-mode fiber
Answer: C
On Monday,Wednesday and Friday a customer completes a backup of only the files that
are changed from the previous full backup.
This is referred to as what type of backup?
A. incremental backup
B. differential backup
C. full backup
D. partial file backup
Answer: D
